1
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:31,280
They're back?

2
00:01:31,280 --> 00:01:32,439
It never ends.

3
00:01:44,200 --> 00:01:44,959
Brother Honghai.

4
00:01:45,439 --> 00:01:46,280
Help me check

5
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:47,280
if there's any

6
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,959
platform similar to DomainNet launching.

7
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,280
Okay.

8
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:58,319
There really is one called eDomainNet.

9
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:01,120
Is its server in Yunhai?

10
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:02,519
How did you know?

11
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,439
In my past life,

12
00:02:04,879 --> 00:02:06,560
this eDomainNet registered in Yunhai

13
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,840
was actually named DomainNet.

14
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:10,879
In this life, I registered DomainNet first.

15
00:02:11,680 --> 00:02:13,759
I wonder which site Wanwang will acquire for a high price.

16
00:02:18,039 --> 00:02:18,919
Not bad.

17
00:02:19,240 --> 00:02:21,159
Giving them a taste of their own medicine.

18
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,199
If they don't play dirty,

19
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,039
I'd be happy to take them on.

20
00:02:47,960 --> 00:02:49,000
I miss my wife so much.

21
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,879
Everyone looks like Ruochu to me.

22
00:02:50,879 --> 00:02:51,319
Chen Fan.

23
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:52,439
Time for breakfast.

24
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,560
Ruochu.

25
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:55,680
Brother Honghai.

26
00:02:56,599 --> 00:02:57,759
What are you doing here?

27
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,599
I bought some breakfast on the way.

28
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,879
I brought some for Brother Honghai too.

29
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:02,560
Thanks.

30
00:03:03,719 --> 00:03:04,319
Ruochu.

31
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,840
You didn't see this kid last night.

32
00:03:05,840 --> 00:03:07,000
The way he fought those hackers...

33
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:08,000
He followed the network cable

34
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,400
and tracked down their IP just like that.

35
00:03:09,639 --> 00:03:10,719
It was so smooth.

36
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,159
Really?

37
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,599
Chen Fan.

38
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:14,879
Have you ever considered

39
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:17,120
applying to Yunhai University's Computer Science Department?

40
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:19,919
And then continue your studies later?

41
00:03:20,599 --> 00:03:21,159
Um...

42
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:23,000
What major do you plan to apply for?

43
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:25,439
I haven't decided yet.

44
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:28,439
I think economics and law are both good.

45
00:03:28,599 --> 00:03:30,080
But my mom wants me to study law.

46
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,280
Chen Fan.

47
00:03:33,639 --> 00:03:34,080
Ruochu.

48
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:37,319
No.

49
00:03:37,560 --> 00:03:38,280
You can't study law.

50
00:03:39,280 --> 00:03:40,080
Chen Fan.

51
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:40,840
What's wrong?

52
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,759
You absolutely cannot study law.

53
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,319
Absolutely not.

54
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,199
What are you doing?

55
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,800
Oh no.

56
00:03:45,319 --> 00:03:46,159
I scared her.

57
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:49,639
Brother Fan.

58
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,560
The exam results are out.

59
00:03:50,719 --> 00:03:51,360
They're out?

60
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:52,560
Got it.

61
00:03:52,879 --> 00:03:53,840
I'll go home and check my score.

62
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,360
What's the score?

63
00:03:57,719 --> 00:03:58,879
Okay, I got it.

64
00:03:58,879 --> 00:03:59,599
Thanks.

65
00:04:01,599 --> 00:04:02,159
How much?

66
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,319
You just said...

67
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,879
what was your score?

68
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:06,240
603.

69
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:08,719
You must have heard wrong.

70
00:04:09,039 --> 00:04:10,240
On your first mock exam,

71
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:11,639
you only got 306.

72
00:04:12,199 --> 00:04:13,159
You just accidentally

73
00:04:14,159 --> 00:04:15,080
scored that high?

74
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:18,240
Then you were way too careless!

75
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:22,040
Our Chen family has produced a college student!

76
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:22,680
That's right.

77
00:04:23,439 --> 00:04:24,360
That's great!

78
00:04:24,439 --> 00:04:25,839
We have to host a banquet for this.

79
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,000
And invite all the relatives over.

80
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:29,040
To have a big celebration.

81
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,040
By the way,

82
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:31,920
where are you going?

83
00:04:32,519 --> 00:04:33,680
I'm going to find a classmate.

84
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,279
What are you doing here?

85
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:41,240
Checked your score?

86
00:04:41,360 --> 00:04:41,759
What's the score?

87
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,720
I got 590.

88
00:04:45,319 --> 00:04:46,120
I heard.

89
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,439
You scored 603.

90
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,120
If you hadn't helped me,

91
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:50,399
I definitely wouldn't have scored this high.

92
00:04:51,279 --> 00:04:52,079
With this score,

93
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,720
you could try applying to China's top universities.

94
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:54,959
I won't go to China's top universities.

95
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,079
I'm going to Yunhai University.

96
00:04:57,879 --> 00:04:58,480
To be with you.

97
00:05:20,639 --> 00:05:21,600
Let go of me

98
00:05:22,639 --> 00:05:23,639
I'll never let go in this life

99
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:24,959
Ruochu

100
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:26,399
I really missed you so much

101
00:05:27,360 --> 00:05:29,000
I've missed you every second of these years

102
00:05:30,839 --> 00:05:32,199
What are you talking about?

103
00:05:32,879 --> 00:05:33,639
Let go of me

104
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:44,800
Chen Fan

105
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:51,079
Now that the college entrance exam is over

106
00:05:51,839 --> 00:05:53,279
There's something I want to tell you

107
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,600
Actually, I'm really ordinary

108
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:59,480
I'm not nearly as good as you imagine

109
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:02,879
Ruochu

110
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,319
My feelings for you...

111
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:05,639
Are far deeper than you imagine

112
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,800
Deep enough to transcend time and space

113
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,000
If it weren't to continue loving you...

114
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:11,959
I wouldn't have come back here

115
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:13,600
I was so scared

116
00:06:14,199 --> 00:06:15,279
I was afraid there wouldn't be enough time

117
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,839
I was afraid I'd wake up from this dream...

118
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:18,480
And you'd disappear from my side again

119
00:06:20,839 --> 00:06:21,879
Promise me one more time

120
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,439
Be my girlfriend

121
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,759
Let's go for walks at Yunhai University together

122
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:29,240
Go to the park bench together

123
00:06:29,439 --> 00:06:30,160
Let's be together

124
00:06:30,160 --> 00:06:30,759
Why?

125
00:06:31,639 --> 00:06:32,600
Why is it...

126
00:06:32,959 --> 00:06:33,360
"Again"?

127
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:37,120
Whether it's "again" or not...

128
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,759
I only want to do these things with you

129
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,160
I want to take everything we didn't get to do...

130
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,399
And everything we did do...

131
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,639
And do it all over again

132
00:06:44,759 --> 00:06:45,279
Okay?

133
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:56,879
I promise you

134
00:06:57,639 --> 00:06:58,199
Really?

135
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:02,040
Then... then I...

136
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,279
Can you keep it down?

137
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:07,519
By the way

138
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:09,839
This is a graduation gift for you

139
00:07:10,199 --> 00:07:11,319
I went and prayed for this

140
00:07:12,079 --> 00:07:12,920
One for each of us

141
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,279
Chen Fan

142
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,079
Today is the day we officially got together

143
00:07:18,759 --> 00:07:21,519
I hope we'll be a couple for a lifetime

144
00:07:22,680 --> 00:07:23,639
And never be apart

145
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:38,160
Just like in the last life

146
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,639
It's back in my hand again

147
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,639
What's wrong?

148
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:42,080
In my last life, just to date Ruochu,

149
00:08:42,399 --> 00:08:43,759
I came to this campus quite a lot.

150
00:08:44,720 --> 00:08:45,200
This time,

151
00:08:45,799 --> 00:08:46,679
Yunhai University,

152
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:47,919
here I come.

153
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:53,559
Excuse me, are you in the Computer Science Department? Hello?

154
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:54,679
Let me see.

155
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:55,840
The dorms are over there.

156
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,399
Hey there.

157
00:08:56,720 --> 00:08:57,279
Need someone to lead the way?

158
00:08:57,399 --> 00:08:57,879
I'll carry your luggage for you.

159
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,639
No need, no need.

160
00:08:58,639 --> 00:08:59,279
Thanks, thanks.

161
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:00,639
It's such a hot day.

162
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,279
Have a bottle of Coke.

163
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:02,039
Cool yourself down.

164
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,679
Thanks.

165
00:09:04,039 --> 00:09:04,320
No problem.

166
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:06,559
Three fifty.

167
00:09:07,159 --> 00:09:07,639
Thanks.

168
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:12,759
Oh.

169
00:09:13,919 --> 00:09:14,440
Thanks.

170
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,000
Here's your change.

171
00:09:16,919 --> 00:09:17,759
Thanks for your patronage.

172
00:09:21,279 --> 00:09:21,960
Hey there.

173
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:22,600
Want a Coke?

174
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,639
This kid is pretty sharp.

175
00:09:24,720 --> 00:09:25,600
We have Sprite too.

176
00:09:28,879 --> 00:09:29,639
Sprite is out.

177
00:09:30,559 --> 00:09:31,120
Darn it.

178
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:33,240
You live in this dorm too?

179
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,159
You study Computer Science too?

180
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,840
Let's reintroduce ourselves.

181
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:37,960
I'm Luo Wenjie.

182
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:39,720
Chen Fan.

183
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:44,639
We're roommates.

184
00:09:45,039 --> 00:09:45,639
I won't make money off you.

185
00:09:45,879 --> 00:09:46,840
No, no, no, no.

186
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,360
Consider it supporting your business.

187
00:09:48,440 --> 00:09:49,279
You take it.

188
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:49,799
Alright.

189
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:51,840
This bottle is on me then.

190
00:09:52,639 --> 00:09:53,240
Drink up.

191
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:56,120
With that sharp brain of yours,

192
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:57,320
you should study economics.

193
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,759
Nah.

194
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:00,960
My family did business when I was young.

195
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:02,519
I just picked it up from them.

196
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,279
True, true.

197
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,080
I heard

198
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:09,120
our third roommate, Liang Shichu,

199
00:10:09,759 --> 00:10:10,519
is really capable.

200
00:10:11,759 --> 00:10:12,840
Seems he's that...

201
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:13,399
Oh.

202
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:15,879
Gold medalist in the National Programming Competition.

203
00:10:16,399 --> 00:10:17,159
He was admitted by recommendation.

204
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,600
Gold medal.

205
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,639
Interesting.

206
00:10:21,399 --> 00:10:23,039
Is there an internet cafe near our school?

207
00:10:23,279 --> 00:10:24,960
There's one just east of the school.

208
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,480
East side, huh.

209
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,879
Pretty intense.

210
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:37,960
Why haven't any buyers come knocking?

211
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,200
Logically speaking,

212
00:10:40,399 --> 00:10:41,720
it's almost the end of September.

213
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:44,519
Many people should be eyeing DomainNet by now.

214
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,120
What new game is this?

215
00:10:47,320 --> 00:10:48,519
This is a website I built myself.

216
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:49,679
I'm checking the backend data.

217
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,360
That's amazing.

218
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,600
I thought you were like the rest of them,

219
00:10:54,399 --> 00:10:55,559
just an internet-addicted teen.

220
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,720
Internet cafes are money trees.

221
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,879
I can't miss out on this.

222
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:08,240
Hello? Ruochu.

223
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,080
Can you hear me?

224
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,200
Chen Fan?

225
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,919
How did you know my number?

226
00:11:13,279 --> 00:11:14,679
I did a little fortune telling.

227
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:15,559
Oh, right.

228
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:18,159
Um, I want to come find you now.

229
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,559
Don't come yet.

230
00:11:20,200 --> 00:11:22,039
My mom dropped me off at school.

231
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:23,799
I have to show her around campus first.

232
00:11:25,000 --> 00:11:25,639
Alright then.

233
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:28,440
Then let's go for a big meal another day.

234
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:28,919
Yeah.

235
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,279
Okay, bye-bye.

236
00:11:33,679 --> 00:11:36,120
Global Village Internet Cafe for Transfer
